  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK338">
<l>kuṭampai taṉittoḻiyap puṭpaṟan taṟṟē</l>
<l>yuṭampō ṭuyiriṭai naṭpu.</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The love of the soul to the body is like (the love of) a bird to its egg which it flies away from and leaves empty.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
